text: Sara López Ravetllat (born 29 November 1992) is a Spanish competitive sailor. She competed at the 2016 Summer Olympics in Rio de Janeiro, in the women's 470 class. ==References== Category:1992 births Category:Living people Category:Spanish female sailors (sport) Category:Olympic sailors of Spain Category:Sailors at the 2016 Summer Olympics – 470
